)
</taxonomicName>
, paralectotypes. C, ovigerous ♀, p1, pereiopod I; p2, pereiopod II; op, operculum; md L, left mandible dorsal view with enlargements of incisor process anterior view and molar process medial view; md R, right mandible dorsal view with enlargements of incisor process anterior view and spine row posterior oblique view. B, copulatory ♂, cv, head ventral view; au, antennula; a, antenna. Scale for habitus, 0.5 mm.
</paragraph>
